SQL_STMT_U.val: select * from (select SW_BIC_CODE, SW_BIC_NAAM1, SW_GRID_CODE, SW_ID from swift_bic_codes s where s.SW_GRID_CODE is not null and SW_BIC_CODE >= '!' and s.SW_BIC_STATUS <= 2 order by SW_ID) where SW_ID >= ~1 and (~2=' ' OR ~2<>' ' and upper(SW_BIC_NAAM1) like ~2 ) fetch first ~3 rows only
